Clint Eastwood put his recently finalised divorce behind him and arrived at the Academy Awards on Sunday with new girlfriend Christina Sandera.

The 84-year-old Hollywood legend looked dapper in a black tuxedo while walking down the red carpet at The Dolby Theater in Los Angeles.

Christina opted for a long-sleeved dark gown with deep V-neck and had her blonde hair down while making her Oscars red carpet debut. 

