The couple at the time had been living together for several months, according to Us Weekly.

Christina was a hostess at Clint's Mission Ranch Hotel in Carmel when they started dating.

Clint previously was married to Maggie Johnson before Dina and also had long relationships with Sondra Locke and Frances Fisher.   

